6.12	Police_Story_(film_series)	Police Story (film series)	The Police Story film series (Chinese: ) comprises five Hong Kong crime-action films, directed by Jackie Chan, Stanley Tong and Benny Chan, produced by Raymond Chow, Leonard Ho, Jackie Chan, Barbie Tung, Willie Chan and Solon So. The first film Police Story was released on 14 December 1985. After the film's success, four sequels were made.	
